# Pitch deliverables that embed prospectus page-crops — keep local-only.
# Issuer holds copyright on the underlying prospectus text/images even
# when the doc is publicly filed at the SEC.
*.pptx

# PDF sources (cache only — re-downloadable from SEC EDGAR / issuer IR).
*.pdf

# Image crops are stored in Supabase Storage (private bucket).
# If anyone runs the harness locally and produces /tmp/evidence/, don't
# accidentally commit those either.
evidence/
